  }, "Finding Upcoming Movies"), mdx("p", null, "This section isn\u2019t super relevant during quarantine, since we\u2019re not going to get huge movie releases in theatres for a while. Still, figuring out what movies are going to be big before they\u2019ve even hit theatres is so exciting! The first thing you need to know is how movies get released."), mdx("p", null, "Most highly anticipated films premiere at ", mdx("strong", {
